text: Thomas Musyl (born 13 January 1967) is an Austrian rower. He competed in the men's double sculls event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1967 births Category:Living people Category:Austrian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Austria Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Neuilly-sur-Seine
